title: Chinese Art by Burling (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Chinese Art
Studio Publications / Thomas Crowell | 1953 | English | 392 pages | PDF | 41.6 MB


There has been a great need for a well illustrated and comprehensive text on every phase of Chinese art with complete and up-to-the minute factual knowledge. This is such a book, and it is written by two famous authorities with sympathy, insight, humor, and deep understanding
